** How Pioneering Physicist Lise Meitner Discovered Nuclear Fission=2C Pav=
ed the Way for Women in Science=2C and Was Denied the Nobel Prize (https:/=
/www.brainpickings.org/2016/10/27/lise-meitner/?utm_source=3DBrain+Picking=
s&utm_campaign=3D073a12b4a0-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2016_10_29&utm_medium=3Demail&u=
tm_term=3D0_179ffa2629-073a12b4a0-236831249&mc_cid=3D073a12b4a0&mc_e=
id=3D[UNIQID])
------------------------------------------------------------

http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0520208609/braipick-20?utm_source=
=3DBrain+Pickings&utm_campaign=3D073a12b4a0-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2016_10_29&utm_=
medium=3Demail&utm_term=3D0_179ffa2629-073a12b4a0-236831249&mc_cid=
