: Georgia=2C serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 175%;text-align: left;">Am=
ong the most outstanding yet under-celebrated of these pioneering women is=
 the Austrian physicist <strong>Lise Meitner</strong> (November 7=2C 1878=
=E2=80=93October 27=2C 1968)=2C who led the team that discovered nuclear f=
