"left" style=3D"-ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;border: 0;height: auto;lin=
e-height: 100%;outline: none;text-decoration: none;padding: 5px 30px 10px=
 0px;display: inline;width: 50px!important;">Lise Meitner: a physicist who=
 never lost her humanity.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"-webkit-text-size-ad=
just: 100%;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #262626;font-family: Georgia=
